Sentencas: This study adopts a novel structure design of large-area planar metal-supported solid oxide fuel cell (MS-SOFC), which exhibits the characteristics of self-sealing and high thermal cycling resistance.
Titulo: Performance and Stability of Plasma-Sprayed 10 x 10 cm2 Self-sealing Metal-Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The self-sealing structure of MS-SOFCs is achieved by brazing technology.
Titulo: Performance and Stability of Plasma-Sprayed 10 x 10 cm2 Self-sealing Metal-Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Plasma spraying is performed to prepare all functional layers of cells.
Titulo: Performance and Stability of Plasma-Sprayed 10 x 10 cm2 Self-sealing Metal-Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The size of cells is 10 x 10 cm(2).
Titulo: Performance and Stability of Plasma-Sprayed 10 x 10 cm2 Self-sealing Metal-Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The coefficients of thermal expansion of relevant parts (i.e., porous metal support, interconnector and compound structure of both) and the electrical conductivity of brazing solder were measured.
Titulo: Performance and Stability of Plasma-Sprayed 10 x 10 cm2 Self-sealing Metal-Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The microstructure of brazing area was observed in situ at 800 degrees C for 500 h, and the distribution of fuel gas in the interconnector was simulated.
Titulo: Performance and Stability of Plasma-Sprayed 10 x 10 cm2 Self-sealing Metal-Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The performance of cells was characterized and found that the maximum power density can reach up to 716 mW cm(-2) at 700 degrees C. Moreover, the long-term stability of the cell was investigated for about 500 h with 6 times of thermal cycling implemented during this period.
Titulo: Performance and Stability of Plasma-Sprayed 10 x 10 cm2 Self-sealing Metal-Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The open circuit voltage and the maximum power density of the cell showed a good stability.
Titulo: Performance and Stability of Plasma-Sprayed 10 x 10 cm2 Self-sealing Metal-Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
